&lt;li&gt;Can adapt to multiple different work environments and settings&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Are customer-oriented with excellent communication skills&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Are a person who is punctual, respectful, and honest with a positive attitude&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Have excellent attention to detail&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Have a strong work ethic&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
